 if you prefer \"Cash App\" you can use: https://cash.me/$Lifeprint\nWant to order a USB drive with four semesters worth of ASL instruction? (ASL 1, ASL 2, ASL 3, and ASL 4)  for $79.95?  \nSee \"SuperUSB\" in the ASLUniversity bookstore at: https://lifeprint.com/bookstore/books...\n\nFor free ASL Lessons see:    / billvicars  \nTo learn basic fingerspelling see    • ABC's in ASL: Learn how to Fingerspell!  \n\nAbout your instructor:\nhttp://www.lifeprint.com/asl101/pages...\nWarm regards and love to you all.\nI am grateful for your support.\nDr. Bill\n:)","commandRuns":[{"startIndex":54,"length":25,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CJYCEM2rARgBIhMIvdm_27frkwMVM6krBh0WoQ4bSMzw-qSmtsWeTcoBBJcD8hU=","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqa29TZ3hVcVR2RDZBWWFIeTVzWXZYaEYxcXpwQXxBQ3Jtc0ttYWg0TzFqRTlHcDVIZHpUamwzcm1haXZvb3ZxRGJDMnVfNW1yMFpPcGsxWU1WV19qMXhJNFdJMmVVUkh5eWpoLXUwM09nZ1VsN1dPendLTUtKeEZHb3hDREM3LUh1Q2dMUGRpQkRvUWVIUGFMblF5VQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=TT0VsmSeuEw","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqa29TZ3hVcVR2RDZBWWFIeTVzWXZYaEYxcXpwQXxBQ3Jtc0ttYWg0TzFqRTlHcDVIZHpUamwzcm1haXZvb3ZxRGJDMnVfNW1yMFpPcGsxWU1WV19qMXhJNFdJMmVVUkh5eWpoLXUwM09nZ1VsN1dPendLTUtKeEZHb3hDREM3LUh1Q2dMUGRpQkRvUWVIUGFMblF5VQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=TT0VsmSeuEw","target":"TARGET_NEW_WINDOW","nofollow":true}}}},{"startIndex":166,"length":40,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CJYCEM2rARgBIhMIvdm_27frkwMVM6krBh0WoQ4bSMzw-qSmtsWeTcoBBJcD8hU=","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbjlXb2Y1ZTMzVkxjTzJjQ09UY0kwaDdBY2x2Z3xBQ3Jtc0tsb2h4dUQ5ejRYSUZGUk8zY21BRkdwVHcxTC1WOUJ4T0RzcjlEel9ETDhDRE1CWHlsdGJ1dVlicXpHd19RN3BQSlNPY